OL,3,CMan charged with 64 offences in
OL,4,Cfuneral home investigation
OL,6,F'254 individual victims': Police
OL,7,Fannounce charges against Robert Bush
OL,9,FA man has been charged with 64
OL,10,Foffences after a 10-month
OL,11,Finvestigation into alleged malpractice
OL,12,Fat a funeral business in Hull.
OL,14,FHumberside Police removed 35 bodies
OL,15,Falong with a quantity of ashes from
OL,16,FLegacy Independent Funeral Directors
OL,17,Fin March last year after concerns were
OL,18,Fraised about care for the deceased.
