OL,6,FAt a joint press conference on
OL,7,FWednesday, Humberside Police and the
OL,8,FCrown Prosecution Service (CPS) said
OL,9,F47-year-old Robert Bush had been
OL,10,Fcharged with 30 counts of preventing a
OL,11,Flawful and decent burial and 30 counts
OL,12,Fof fraud by false representation.
OL,14,FHe is also charged with two counts of
OL,15,Ftheft from charities, one count of
OL,16,Ffraudulent trading in relation to
OL,17,Ffuneral plans for 172 people.
OL,19,FMr Bush, of Kirk Ella, also faces one
OL,20,Fcharge of fraud in relation to human
OL,21,Fashes involving 50 alleged victims.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
