OL,4,Cfuneral home investigation
OL,6,FHe has been bailed to appear at Hull
OL,7,FMagistrates' Court charged on 25 June.
OL,9,FDeputy Chief Constable Dave Marshall
OL,10,Fsaid: "We have updated the families of
OL,11,Fthe 35 deceased with this development
OL,12,Fand we have made initial contact with
OL,13,Fadditional victims who have been
OL,14,Faffected by the investigation and we
OL,15,Fwill be personally in touch with them
OL,16,Fin the coming days.
