OL,6,F"As the investigation now moves into
OL,7,Fthe courts and judicial process, I
OL,8,Fwould please ask people to refrain
OL,9,Ffrom any speculation or commenting
OL,10,Fthat could prejudice or jeopardise the
OL,11,Fcase, and to allow those affected to
OL,12,Fget the answers they desperately need
OL,13,Fand rightly deserve."
OL,15,FThe investigation was launched on 6
OL,16,FMarch 2024 after a report was made to
OL,17,Fpolice expressing concern about the
OL,18,F"storage and management processes
OL,19,Frelating to the care of the deceased"
OL,20,Fat Legacy.
