OL,4,Cfuneral home investigation
OL,6,FPolice later described it as a "truly
OL,7,Fhorrific incident".
OL,9,FIn July last year the force said it
OL,10,Fhad identified 163 families thought to
OL,11,Fbe connected to the ashes removed from
OL,12,Fthe funeral home, but confirmed it was
OL,13,Fimpossible to identify the ashes using
OL,14,FDNA.
OL,16,FIn January detectives said 13,000
OL,17,Fexhibits had been passed to the CPS
OL,18,Ffollowing a "meticulous" investigation.
OL,20,FHull West and Haltemprice MP Emma
OL,21,FHardy welcomed the news of the charges.
