OL,6,FShe said: "The awful events
OL,7,Fsurrounding Legacy Independent Funeral
OL,8,FDirectors have caused untold pain and
OL,9,Fsuffering to people in our community.
OL,11,F"While nothing will take away the
OL,12,Fheartache the families of the victims
OL,13,Fand those who were misled into giving
OL,14,Ftheir hard earned savings to ensure
OL,15,Fthey received a dignified send off
OL,16,Ffeel, it is a step closer to the
OL,17,Fjustice they and their family members
OL,18,Fdeserve."
OL,20,FA 55-year-old woman arrested in July
OL,21,F2024 has been released without charge.
